        <updateDate>2023-09-21T13:44:44Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Deterring Egregious State Infiltration of Schools' Training Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill prohibits the U.S. military departments from establishing or maintaining a Junior Reserve Officers' Training Corps (JROTC) unit at an educational institution that is owned, operated, or controlled by China, a member of the Chinese Community Party or the Chinese military, or a Chinese military company. &lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
